{"type":"message","id":"b2bcaed5","parentId":"8c6eca11","timestamp":"2026-03-18T18:48:52.693Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我是 **Kimi K2.5**（Moonshot 的模型）🌙\n\n目前在 OpenClaw 里我的配置是 `moonshot/kimi-k2.5`，也是这个工作空间的默认模型。\n\n需要我切换成其他模型吗？OpenClaw 支持的选项有：\n- **GLM-Flash** - 超快响应\n- **GLM-Plus** - 更强的推理能力\n- **Qwen3-8B** - 本地运行，隐私更好\n\n用 `/status` 或 `/model <模型名>` 就能查看或切换。需要我帮你换吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":460,"output":132,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773859728740}}
